listings.comment: Overall a good experience - very prompt in his response time and pleasant communication. Details regarding the form were not understood (the text above the form and below the form I requested where not added. Also the form had a "message" field that was not required. This is likely due to working with templates - which is fine. Attention to detail needs improvement. Thank you for your services.
I could not find what was my website's problem. He did some research and found problems. After that, he found a solution to a challenging issue.
This collaboration was very Nice. He is a kind and very helpful person, very responsive and available. He helps me to make 2 pages of my new Website on Webflow.

I am absolutely thrilled with the work he has done! He took the time to truly listen to my needs and delivered beyond my expectations. My website is perfect! As an esthetician offering a wide range of treatments, it was a huge project, and he exceeded every expectation I had. I’m so happy with the result and I have no regrets at all. Highly recommend his services!

Working with this individual was very frustrating. We documented every single revision necessary — he often missed entire sections or said they were done and they were incomplete. He also sent an update to us on work he’s doing for another client, showing lack of professionalism and further intention to detail. 

The worst part: he published the draft in progress website live, and didn’t realize what he did and didn’t know how to correct it. 

Have never worked with someone I’ve rated this poorly. We were extremely disappointed in the end and took many matters into our own hands to fix just to get the project finished.
